---
import OleloPhrase from "./ui/OleloPhrase.astro";
---
<section class="section paper-noise">
  <div class="container-x grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-start">
    <div class="md:col-span-3">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-lava">
        Mission
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-9">
      <p class="font-display text-display-md md:text-display-lg leading-[1.05] text-ink"
         style="text-wrap: balance; font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 96;">
        We exist to make it
        <span class="italic text-ulu">easier and fairer</span> to run a food truck in Hawai‘i —
        and to make sure every island gets the food, the gathering, and the
        <em class="italic text-lava not-italic-children">mākaukau</em>
        <span class="sr-only">(readiness, preparation)</span>
        that comes with it.
      </p>

      <hr class="rule my-10" />

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-sm md:text-base text-stone">
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink/80 mb-2">For the vendors</p>
          <p>Permits, training, signage, and a network. Less time on paperwork; more time at the window.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink/80 mb-2">For the public</p>
          <p>Rallies, mini-docs, and a discovery app so finding the truck you love is one tap, not one rumor.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink/80 mb-2">For Hawai‘i</p>
          <p>Local money stays local. Street food keeps its place as part of who we are.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-10 text-sm">
        <OleloPhrase haw="E ʻai i ka mea i loaʻa" en="Eat what you have — be grateful for the food in front of you." />
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
